> 
> - from:
> 
> ```text
> libRblas.dylib -> libRblas.0.dylib
> ```
> 
> - to:
> 
> ```text
> libRblas.dylib -> libRblas.vecLib.dylib
> ```
> 
> After that single change, the `R 4.5.3` runtime regained the fast timings:
> 
> ```text
> R version 4.5.3 (2026-03-11)
> crossprod vec
> user system elapsed
> 0.032 0.002 0.033
> matmult
> user system elapsed
> 0.055 0.003 0.032
